### [Esther Chapter 3](../../../bib/kjv/est003.htm#001.md)

[Esther](../../../bib/kjv/est001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">est 3:0</span></span>

Overview

[Est 3:1](../../../bib/kjv/est003.htm#001.md), Haman, advanced by the king,
and despised by Mordecai, seeks revenge upon all the Jews; [Est
3:7](../../../bib/kjv/est003.htm#007.md), He casts lots; [Est
3:8](../../../bib/kjv/est003.htm#008.md), He obtains by calumniation a
decree of the king to put the Jews to death.

